description: Fight. Survive. Repeat. #BlackOps6 marks the epic return of @Treyarch's Round-Based Zombies 🧟
title: Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 - Official Round Based Zombies Terminus Reveal Trailer | New Gameplay

description:
Treyarch is bringing back its iconic zombies mode for Call of Duty: Black Ops 6, and it just might be the mode's biggest outing yet. 

We played an hour of Black Ops 6's Terminus map to get a sense of the new features Treyarch is bringing with the return of round-based Zombies. Treyarch is instituting a ton of adjustments and additions to its Zombies mode to make it more approachable for new players and more intense for the hardcore set.

#gaming #callofduty #gamespot
title: Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 Zombies Is Bigger Than Ever

description:
In Splitgate 2, each faction has its own strengths and playstyle, which players are free to explore and discover. Switch between factions, mix and match factions when you team up with your friends, and find the one that fits how you want to frag.

Watch Splitgate 2 live for the first time. August 14 @ 12PM PT / 3PM ET.
